---

<Layout 
  title="Trail Running in Vietnam" 
  description="Discover Vietnam's best trail running routes through mountains, jungles, and rice terraces. Find detailed guides for runners of all levels."
  image="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1528127269322-539801943592"
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <HeroSection
    title="Trail Running in Vietnam"
    subtitle="Explore spectacular running trails through mountains, rice terraces, and lush forests"
    backgroundImage="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1528127269322-539801943592"
    buttonText="Find Your Trail"
    buttonLink="#trails"
  />
  
  <!-- Introduction -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-inter font-bold mb-6">Run Wild in Vietnam</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-text/80 mb-4">
          Vietnam offers a trail runner's paradise with diverse terrain ranging from the rugged mountains of the north to the lush jungles of the central highlands and coastal paths of the south.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-text/80">
          Whether you're looking for a challenging mountain ascent or a scenic run through terraced rice fields, our trail running guides provide everything you need to lace up and explore Vietnam on foot.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Filter Section -->
  <section id="trails" class="py-12 bg-background">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-inter font-bold mb-8">Explore Trail Running Routes</h2>
      
      <FilterBar 
        difficulties={[
          { value: 'easy', label: 'Easy' },
          { value: 'moderate', label: 'Moderate' },
          { value: 'difficult', label: 'Difficult' },
          { value: 'challenging', label: 'Challenging' },
        ]}
        durations={durations}
        regions={regions}
        activities={terrainTypes}
      />
      
      <!-- Trail Running Adventures -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {trails.map(trail => (
          <AdventureCard
            title={trail.title}
            location={trail.location}
            difficulty={trail.difficulty}
            duration={trail.duration}
            image={trail.image}
            link={trail.link}
            featured={trail.featured}
          />
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Trail Running Tips -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-inter font-bold mb-6">Trail Running in Vietnam: Tips & Insights</h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="flex">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 mr-4">
                <div class="bg-primary/10 w-12 h-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-inter text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Best Seasons</h3>
                <p class="text-text/80">Northern Vietnam: September-November and March-May. Central and Southern: November-April. Avoid the summer monsoon season for mountain trails.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 mr-4">
                <div class="bg-primary/10 w-12 h-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M20.354 15.354A9 9 0 018.646 3.646 9.003 9.003 0 0012 21a9.003 9.003 0 008.354-5.646z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-inter text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Weather Preparation</h3>
                <p class="text-text/80">Mornings can be cool in mountain regions even during summer. Pack layers and always bring rain protection, especially during shoulder seasons.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 mr-4">
                <div class="bg-primary/10 w-12 h-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-inter text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Local Running Groups</h3>
                <p class="text-text/80">Connect with Vietnam Trail Runners, Saigon Runners, or Hanoi Trail Addicts on Facebook to find group runs and local race events.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 mr-4">
                <div class="bg-primary/10 w-12 h-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-inter text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Safety Essentials</h3>
                <p class="text-text/80">Carry sufficient water, electrolytes, and energy snacks. Bring a fully charged phone, trail map, and first aid basics. Consider trekking poles for steep terrain.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="relative">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1452626038306-9aae5e071dd3" 
            alt="Trail runner in Vietnam mountains"
            class="rounded-lg shadow-xl object-cover h-[500px] w-full"
          />
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-lg max-w-xs hidden md:block">
            <p class="font-inter font-semibold mb-1">Annual Trail Races</p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-text/80">
              <li>• Vietnam Mountain Marathon (September)</li>
              <li>• Vietnam Jungle Marathon (May)</li>
              <li>• Sapa Ultra Trail (November)</li>
              <li>• Da Lat Ultra Trail (March)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Trail Running Essential Gear -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-background">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-inter font-bold mb-10 text-center">Essential Trail Running Gear</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <div class="bg-primary/10 w-16 h-16 mx-auto rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-inter font-semibold mb-2 text-center">Clothing</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Moisture-wicking shirts</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Lightweight running shorts/tights</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Trail running socks</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Light rain jacket</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <div class="bg-primary/10 w-16 h-16 mx-auto rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-inter font-semibold mb-2 text-center">Footwear</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Trail running shoes with grip</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Gaiters for muddy trails</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Extra shoelaces</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Anti-blister balm</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <div class="bg-primary/10 w-16 h-16 mx-auto rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 15a4 4 0 004 4h9a5 5 0 10-.1-9.999 5.002 5.002 0 10-9.78 2.096A4.001 4.001 0 003 15z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-inter font-semibold mb-2 text-center">Hydration & Nutrition</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Hydration pack (1.5-2L)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Electrolyte tablets</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Energy gels/bars</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Water purification tabs</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
